<section id="Section520094">
    <title>
      <anchor id="Anchor595488" role="Index"
              xreflabel="costing:history by item;item costs:history of"/> 
      <indexterm significance="normal">
        <primary>costing</primary>

        <secondary>history by item</secondary>
      </indexterm> 
      <indexterm significance="normal">
        <primary>item costs</primary>

        <secondary>history of</secondary>
      </indexterm>Item Costs History</title>

    <para id="Para520095">The "Item Costs History" display features an
    historical record of Costs per Item, sorted by Costing Elements. To view
    the history of Costs associated with an individual Item, select the "Item
    Costs History" option. The following screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para520099">
      <screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
               <imagedata fileref="images/PD_Cost_dispItemCostHist.png" id="Graphic563475"/>
            </imageobject>

            <caption id="Caption520100">Item Costs History</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot>
   </para>

    <para id="Para520106">When displaying the history of Costs associated with
    an Item, you are presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520107">Item Number</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x19234c8">
            <para>Enter the Item Number of the Item whose Cost history you would
          like to view.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para663317">UOM</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923510">
            <para>Inventory Unit of Measure.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520111">Costing History</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923558">
            <para>Display lists an Item's Cost History, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para520113">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520114">CLOSE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x19235c4">
            <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para663977">PRINT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192360c">
            <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>